	$ = skuid.$;



var model = skuid.model.getModel("TestingSlot");
var row = model.getFirstRow();

	
label= 'label_Testing?id=' + row.Id;


console.log('Calling Print Command');
top.document.getElementById('pdf').setAttribute("src",label);
setTimeout(function(){callPrint("pdf");},500);
    

function callPrint(iframeId) {
      var PDF = document.getElementById(iframeId);
      PDF.focus();
      PDF.contentWindow.print();
      skuid.$('.ui-dialog-content').dialog('close');  

  }</jsitem><jsitem location="inlinesnippet" name="reloadScreen" cachelocation="false">var params = arguments[0],

location.reload();</jsitem><jsitem location="inlinesnippet" name="getLicenseAndLoad" cachelocation="false">var params = arguments[0],
	$ = skuid.$;
	
var model = skuid.model.getModel("DriversLicense");
var row = model.getFirstRow();
var DL = row.DLScan;

var result = DL.split("\n");
console.log(result);

row.FirstName = result[5].substring(3,result[5].length);
row.LastName = result[3].substring(3,result[3].length);
row.MiddleName = result[7].substring(3,result[7].length);
row.Address = result[18].substring(3,result[18].length);
row.City = result[19].substring(3,result[19].length);
row.State = result[20].substring(3,result[20].length);
row.Zip = result[21].substring(3,result[21].length-4);

model.save();
console.log(row.data);
